Package: disdRo
Type: Package
Title: Functions for working with disdrometric data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Santiago", "Beguería", email="santiago.begueria@csic.es", role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Borja", "Latorre", email="santiago.begueria@csic.es", role="aut"),
    person("Marta", "Angulo-Martínez", email="santiago.begueria@csic.es", role="ctb"))
Description: A set of functions for reading and handling meteor drop size and velocity distribution (DSVD), or disdrometric matrix data, from raw data files generated by Thies LPM or Ott Parsivel optical disdrometers.
